Content-Type: text/plain;
 charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit

Greetings,

Could someone comment on the time frame for the next Cantera release? Our
team is successfully using the latest development version, however, we would
like to move to a stable released version.

Also, what is the required manner in which the use of Cantera should be
displayed if, for example, an application code is using Cantera as a TPL?
Currently, we simply have a list of all TPLs that our application uses with
version number. Should we include something more?

With best wishes,

Stefan

--B_3245305066_15731013
